    <title>Hexo+Github搭建博客教程</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/04/17/Hexo-Github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/04/17/Hexo-Github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</id>
    <published>2020-04-16T17:42:58.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-21T12:09:03.048Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h2><p>先下载git</p><ul><li>下载git<br><a href="https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/git-for-windows/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">git下载</a></li><li>下载Node<br><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">node下载</a></li></ul><p>下载完成之后使用 <code>win + R</code>，输入<code>cmd</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;查看是否存在对应的版本号</span><br><span class="line">git -v</span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在你想要安装<code>Hexo</code>的位置新建文件夹<code>Hexo</code>，右键选择<code>Git Bash Here</code>，输入</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看<code>Hexo</code>是否安装成功</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再次输入<code>hexo init</code>初始化<code>hexo</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动服务依次输入</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;安装所需要的组件</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输入<code>hexo g</code>，首次体验<code>Hexo</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输入<code>hexo s</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;启动服务</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在浏览器输入该网址正式体验<code>Hexo</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http:&#x2F;&#x2F;localhost:4000&#x2F;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时此刻就能在浏览器看到我们搭建的博客网站。</p><h2 id="可能会出现的问题"><a href="#可能会出现的问题" class="headerlink" title="可能会出现的问题"></a>可能会出现的问题</h2><p>界面出现</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;%- partial(&#39;_partial&#x2F;head&#39;) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;%- partial(&#39;_partial&#x2F;header&#39;, null, &#123;cache: !config.relative_link&#125;) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;%- body %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;% if (theme.sidebar &amp;&amp; theme.sidebar !&#x3D;&#x3D; &#39;bottom&#39;)&#123; %&gt; &lt;%- partial(&#39;_partial&#x2F;sidebar&#39;, null, &#123;cache: !config.relative_link&#125;) %&gt; &lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;%- partial(&#39;_partial&#x2F;footer&#39;, null, &#123;cache: !config.relative_link&#125;) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;%- partial(&#39;_partial&#x2F;mobile-nav&#39;, null, &#123;cache: !config.relative_link&#125;) %&gt; &lt;%- partial(&#39;_partial&#x2F;after-footer&#39;) %&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>是因为没有安装好<code>Hexo</code>渲染的插件，因该是漏掉了<code>hexo install</code>步骤</p><h2 id="将博客托管到Github上"><a href="#将博客托管到Github上" class="headerlink" title="将博客托管到Github上"></a>将博客托管到Github上</h2><blockquote><p>确认自己的已经配置好了 git全局信息 和 SSH Key</p></blockquote><p>在<code>github</code>上新建一个仓库，以我的<code>github</code>名字为例</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;命名方式（github名称+.github.io）</span><br><span class="line">Onesanpang.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开<code>Hexo</code>文件下<code>_config.yml</code>配置文件（最好用<code>sublime</code>）找到<code>deploy</code>进行如下配置</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;qiuyeyijian&#x2F;Onesanpang.github.io.git   &#x2F;&#x2F;将地址换成自己的</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  &#x2F;&#x2F;请注意</span><br><span class="line">  &#x2F;&#x2F;冒号后面一定要有一个空格</span><br><span class="line">  &#x2F;&#x2F;type，repository，branch的首字母要对齐</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行下面三个命令</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">运行：npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line">运行：hexo g  &#x2F;&#x2F;（本地生成静态文件）</span><br><span class="line">运行：hexo d  &#x2F;&#x2F;（将本地静态文件推送至Github）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开浏览器，访问<a href="http://Onesanpang.github.io即可" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://Onesanpang.github.io即可</a></p><h2 id="Hexo基础配置"><a href="#Hexo基础配置" class="headerlink" title="Hexo基础配置"></a>Hexo基础配置</h2><p>当我们成功地将博客托管到了<code>Github</code>上面了之后，需要对博客进行基础地配置。打开<code>Hexo</code>文件下下面的<code>_config.yml</code>。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Site</span><br><span class="line">title: Onesanpang &#x2F;&#x2F;博客名字</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: &#39;&#39;</span><br><span class="line">description: &#39;&#39;</span><br><span class="line">keywords:</span><br><span class="line">author: Zhby &#x2F;&#x2F;作者</span><br><span class="line">language: zh-Hans &#x2F;&#x2F;语言</span><br><span class="line">timezone: &#39;&#39; </span><br><span class="line">theme: next &#x2F;&#x2F;主题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里主题我用的是<code>next</code>主题，更多主题在下面可以进行下载</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hexo.io&#x2F;themes&#x2F;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载<code>next</code>主题方式</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;iissnan&#x2F;hexo-theme-nextthemes&#x2F;next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载好了之后在<code>_config.yml</code>将主题改成<code>next</code>。</p><h3 id="标签、分类、关于"><a href="#标签、分类、关于" class="headerlink" title="标签、分类、关于"></a>标签、分类、关于</h3><p>打开在<code>next</code>文件下的<code>_config.yml</code><br>···<br>menu:<br>  //注意||两边的空格要去掉<br>  home: /||home<br>  tags: /tags/||tags<br>  categories: /categories/||th<br>  archives: /archives/<br>  about: /about/||user<br>···</p><p>分类和标签只需要在使用在<code>Hexo</code>文件下运行下面的命令</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">D:\hexo\blog&gt;hexo new page &quot;about&quot;</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: D:\hexo\blog\source\about\index.md</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">D:\hexo\blog&gt;hexo new page &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: D:\hexo\blog\source\tags\index.md</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">D:\hexo\blog&gt;hexo new page &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: D:\hexo\blog\source\categories\index.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;运行之后，会在会再source文件下创建about、tags、categories文件夹，每个文件夹下还会创建一个index.md文件。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还差最后一步，打开各页面对应的index.md文件，编辑如下内容，title和date是默认生成的，增加type即可</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: about</span><br><span class="line">date: 2019-06-25 19:16:17</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;about&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: about</span><br><span class="line">date: 2019-06-25 19:16:17</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: about</span><br><span class="line">date: 2019-06-25 19:16:17</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到这里，这些基础配置就差不多了。当然，如果想要我们的博客更加的完美我们继续往后操作。</p><h2 id="Hexo-Next-主题配置"><a href="#Hexo-Next-主题配置" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Next 主题配置"></a>Hexo Next 主题配置</h2><p>可以查看这博客<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/9f0e90cc32c2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo-NexT配置超炫网页效果</a></p><p>其中添加访问数量打开<code>next</code>主题配置文件<code>\themes\next_config.yml</code>，搜索找到<code>busuanzi_count</code>，把<code>enable</code>设置为<code>true</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; next 6.0 的配置样式</span><br><span class="line">busuanzi_count:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_visitors: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_visitors_icon: user</span><br><span class="line">  total_views: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_views_icon: eye</span><br><span class="line">  post_views: true</span><br><span class="line">  post_views_icon: eye</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; next 5.0 的配置样式</span><br><span class="line">busuanzi_count:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  site_uv: true</span><br><span class="line">  site_uv_header: &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-user&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 本站访问数</span><br><span class="line">  site_uv_footer: 人</span><br><span class="line">  site_pv: true</span><br><span class="line">  site_pv_header: &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-eye&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 本站总访问量</span><br><span class="line">  site_pv_footer: 次</span><br><span class="line">  page_pv: false</span><br><span class="line">  page_pv_header: &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-file-o&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 本文总阅读量</span><br><span class="line">  page_pv_footer: 次</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>配置完了之后发现不能正常显示的话可能是引用地址更换了，检查<code>themes\next\layout_third-party\analytics\busuanzi-counter.swig</code>文件，更换引用地址为：<code>https://busuanzi.ibruce.info/busuanzi/2.3/busuanzi.pure.mini.js</code>。即可</p>]]></content>
    
